title: Just Do It! | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Just Do It! | Joel Osteen
description:
There is a blessing attached to every act of obedience. When you do what God has asked you to do even when you don't understand, you're positioning yourself for a new level of your destiny.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
